      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 it's a functional, drivable car that has seen its share of use and shows it. Expect visible wear on the exterior, including some scratches, minor dents, and paint scuffs consistent with everyday driving over the years. The interior is serviceable but worn \u2014 you'll notice fading, some scuffs on trim pieces, and upholstery that reflects regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives without major issues, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance attention in the near future. This is an honest, straightforward vehicle for a buyer who wants reliable transportation at an accessible price point and doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
