    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Reliable \u2013 A Great Everyday Driver! \ud83d\ude97 Here's a genuinely good car at an honest price! This vehicle is in good condition overall \u2014 it drives well, has been maintained, and presents nicely both inside and out. You'll find some minor wear consistent with normal use, but nothing that takes away from its reliability or appeal. No major mechanical issues, no hidden surprises \u2014 just a dependable ride ready for its next owner. If you're looking for a trustworthy used car that won't let you down, this one deserves a serious look! Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 an outstanding example that stands apart on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or fading, and all body panels are straight and true with consistent panel gaps throughout. The interior is immaculate \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all trim pieces show no meaningful wear, staining, or damage, presenting like a nearly new cabin. Mechanically, this car is in top form: the engine starts instantly, runs smoothly and quietly, and all systems \u2014 transmission, brakes, suspension, HVAC, electronics \u2014 function exactly as intended with no known issues. Service history has been well maintained, and this vehicle is ready to drive with complete confidence from day one. If you're looking for a used car that truly delivers a like-new experience, this is a rare find worth serious consideration.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is offered as a reliable, drivable used car with honest acknowledgment of its wear and imperfections. The exterior shows multiple scratches, a few small dents, and some paint fading across various panels \u2014 nothing structurally compromising, but cosmetically noticeable. The interior shows clear signs of use, including worn upholstery, some scuffs on the dashboard and door panels, and general wear consistent with its age and mileage. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some components may be approaching the end of their service life and routine maintenance or minor repairs could be needed in the near term. All four tires have usable tread remaining, though they are not new. This is a solid option for a buyer seeking an affordable, functional vehicle who is comfortable with cosmetic imperfections and understands they are purchasing a used car in everyday, well-worn condition. A pre-purchase inspection is welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    }
